data.description:
Incredible Value! Price Reduced for Quick Sale!

Don't miss out on the chance to call this meticulously maintained 4BR/2.5 BA craftsman your new home. Nestled in the desirable Canterbury Farms neighborhood, this property offers a unique blend of style, comfort, and functionality.

As you approach, a charming front porch beckons you inside, where you'll be greeted by the warmth of beautiful hardwood floors that seamlessly traverse the main level. This spacious area encompasses a formal dining room, a cozy living room, a versatile office space, a convenient mudroom, and a bright eat-in kitchen.

The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting pristine white cabinetry, top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, expansive granite countertops, and a stunning tiled backsplash. Elegant pendant lights hang over a generously sized kitchen island, creating the ideal setting for hosting unforgettable gatherings with friends and family.

Upstairs, you'll discover a plush carpeted floor housing three generously sized bedrooms. They share a tiled laundry room and a stylish hall bathroom featuring a double vanity bowl. The pièce de résistance is the master bedroom, which includes an ensuite bathroom complete with a double raised marble vanity, exquisite tiled floors, a luxurious glass walk-in shower, a relaxing garden tub, and a spacious walk-in closet.

Step outside to your private haven, where a vast, fenced-in backyard awaits. It's the perfect playground for children and pets, offering safety and freedom to roam. Enjoy the covered porch, an idyllic space for hosting family gatherings, entertaining friends, or savoring quiet evenings with a barbecue.

This home is not only stunning but also environmentally conscious, with features like low VOC paint for better indoor air quality, a radiant energy barrier in the roofing system, and energy-efficient windows and doors. The two-car attached garage is the cherry on top, ensuring you stay dry during those rainy days.

With a reduced price, this remarkable property won't stay on the market for long. Seize the opportunity to make this house your forever home and experience the Canterbury Farms lifestyle to the fullest.
